### Environment
# Uses `.vscode/rest-client.env.json` variables
# Set `employeeApiBase` in the `local` or `customPort` environment.

### Health check
GET {{employeeApiBase}}/api/employees/health
Accept: application/json

### Swagger UI
GET {{employeeApiBase}}/swagger

### Weather (template)
GET {{employeeApiBase}}/weatherforecast/
Accept: application/json

